author: phred
msg: Matt Sergeant has graciously donated Apache::Reload to the ASF.  This commit
moves Apache2::Reload from the mod_perl core to the Apache::Reload distribution,
including svn mv's of a few files in changeset 606232 from the mod_perl core
Reviewed in part by Gozer, Phillip, and Geoff.

author: phred
msg: Apache2::Reload is being moved to an externally maintained CPAN distribution.
Apache::Reload has been graciously donated to the ASF by Matt Sergeant.  This
commit is part of an svn mv of related files to that distribution.
